<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Lorenz Deinsdorfer und Götz Grieß</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er derzeit keiner Diener bedarf.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_579" id="288v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_579_r1l13">Lorencʒen <expan>Teynſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l14">Göcʒen Grieſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_579_r1l15"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> lorencʒ vnd Göcʒ als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt vvıe Jr <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l16">reıten . vnd vns dıenen wöltet etc Das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l17">Vnd <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch des mıt fleıſſ / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l18">ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> niht leẅt beſtellen . wurden wır <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> hernach mer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_line_1592207045334_4228">leẅt . <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol gedacht ſeın . daʒ Jr eẅch alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l21"><expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> vns <expan>erpotte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / Vnd wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_579_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_579" id="288v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Lorenczen <expan>Teynstorff<ex>er</ex></expan> und Göczen Griessen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> Lorencz und Göcz, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu uns reiten und uns dienen wöltet etc.,
                        das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch des mit fleiss; und
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht lewt bestellen. Wurden
                        wir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> hernach mer lewt
                            <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan>, so <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        wol gedacht sein, daz ir ewch also <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> uns
                                <expan>erpotte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt; und wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
